metadata.name: Home (Epic)
metadata.description:
Lowly's Library of Lyricism.

This is an official, one of one lyric sheet from Jacob Lee's lyrical archive. This NFT does not provide commercial or licensing rights to either the track or lyrics. Each NFT in this collection represents a specific song within Jacob Lee's existing music catalogue. It also grants access to Lowly's Library in the Metaverse. 

Lyrics conceptualised by Jacob Lee. Artwork by Maahy Abdul.
